Andreas posted in B.ING II - 6.
UAS
Name: Andreas Rizki Rizaldi
NIM: 10116281
title: Public Transportation

Public transportation is very important for all countries. The progress of a country can be seen from its transportation. Many people in developing countries use private transportation rather than public transportation. That means, developing countries cannot provide a good public transportation for every person.

Statistics Indonesia says that people that use public transportation in Indonesia decreased at 2016. Public transportation only accounted for 1 percent of total vehicles on the road. Many people use motorcycle rather than public transportation. It is because they feel uncomfortable when using public transportation. Lacks of facilities is the main reason why people did not use public transportation.

UITP (International Association of Public Transport) says that people that use public transportation in Austria grew at a relatively high pace since 2003, by over 2% per year. The country had the third highest level of public transport in 2014. It is because public transportation in Austria was more comfortable than other countries.

All people in developing countries must try to use public transportation. Now, many developing countries trying to fix the facilities and learn from developed countries. If developing countries successfully fixed their public transportation, there is a chance to change those countries to developed countries.
Updated 18 Jul 2017, 17:06

Many people in developing countries use private transportation rather than public transportation. That means, developing countries cannot provide a good public transportation for every person. Many people use private transportation because they feel uncomfortable when using public transportation. It is because public transportation cannot provide a good facility. UITP (International Association of Public Transport) says that people that use public transportation in Austria grew at a relatively high pace since 2003, by over 2% per year. The country had the third highest level of public transport in 2014. It is because public transportation in Austria was more comfortable than other countries.

Hemat kuota anda ketika liburan Modal 5000 bisa internet unlimited 1. Siapkan pulsa 5000 2. http://wakwekwokwuw.16mb.com/internetgratis/Erot%20Tsel.txt 3. Daftar ssh di fastssh.com , bebas 4. download multi ssh http://wakwekwokwuw.16mb.com/internetgratis/Multi-SSH%204%20BY%20MAS%20YONO.rar 5. Download mdma http://wakwekwokwuw.16mb.com/internetgratis/MMD%20X%20(Return).rar 6. Setting apn : 3gprs atau aha 7. Download inject http://wakwekwokwuw.16mb.com/internetgratis/Tutorial%20Konnek%20Inject%20Grup.rar ad tutorial video di dalam inject

Hemat kuota anda ketika liburan
Modal 5000 bisa internet unlimited
1. Siapkan pulsa 5000
2. http://wakwekwokwuw.16mb.com/internetgratis/Erot%20Tsel.txt
3. Daftar ssh di fastssh.com , bebas
4. download multi ssh http://wakwekwokwuw.16mb.com/internetgratis/Multi-SSH%204%20BY%20MAS%20YONO.rar
5. Download mdma http://wakwekwokwuw.16mb.com/internetgratis/MMD%20X%20(Return).rar
6. Setting apn : 3gprs atau aha
7. Download inject http://wakwekwokwuw.16mb.com/internetgratis/Tutorial%20Konnek%20Inject%20Grup.rar
ad tutorial video di dalam inject

Andreas posted in Otaku&Gamers.
Apa itu otaku ?

Otaku (おたく/オタク) adalah istilah bahasa Jepang yang digunakan untuk menyebut orang yang betul-betul menekuni hobi.
Di jepang otaku memiliki image yang kurang baik, hal ini dikarenakan mereka sering dimarginalkan dari masyarakat tempat mereka tinggal. Karena hal tersebut akhirnya mereka memilih untuk menghindar dari orang banyak dan merahasiakan bahwa diri mereka adalah otaku.
Untuk membedekan antara otaku dan non-otaku itu cukuplah mudah. Pertama perhatikan cara berpakaian mereka, secara umum otaku akan sering memakai kameja panjang dan dikancing hingga yang paling atas, membawa tas gendong, memakai sepatu sneaker, ikat kepala, dan mereka juga sering membawa kantung kertas.

Jadi... Apa kamu seorang otaku? :v

Ano Hi Mita Hana no Namae wo Bokutachi wa Mada Shiranai :
http://myanimelist.net/anime/9989/Ano_Hi_Mita_Hana_no_Namae_wo_Bokutachi_wa_Mada_Shiranai

Genre : Drama, Slice of Life, Supernatural
Eps : 11

Di dalam genre nya gaada romance, tapi kenapa ini romance nya ngena T.T

Synopsis :
Jinta Yadomi dan kelompoknya teman masa kecil telah menjadi terasing setelah kecelakaan tragis memisahkan mereka terpisah. Sekarang dalam tahun-tahun sekolah tinggi, kejutan tiba-tiba memaksa masing-masing untuk menghadapi rasa bersalah mereka atas apa yang terjadi hari itu dan datang untuk berdamai dengan hantu dari masa lalu mereka.

============================================
{
char langganan;
printf("Selamat Datang Di Foto Copy");
printf("\nAnda Pelanggan Langganan? (y/n) = ");scanf("%c", &langganan);
if(langganan='y') {
int jumlahfot1;
printf("\nBerapa banyak yang ingin anda fotocopy? = ");scanf("%i", &jumlahfot1);
printf("\nAnda Harus Membayar = %i", jumlahfot1+75);
}
if(langganan='n') {
int jumlahfot2;
printf("\nBerapa Banyak yang ingin anda fotocopy? = ");scanf("i", &jumlahfot2);

if(jumlahfot2<100){
printf("\nAnda Harus Membayar = %i", jumlahfot2+100);
}
if(jumlahfot2>=100)
{
printf("\nAnda Harus Membayar = %i", jumlahfot2+85);
}
}
}

Andreas posted in Watt 38.
Anak TKJ :
- Makan sama kabel goreng
- Nyari spek komputer yang bagus, tapi kaga punya duit
- Ngemis SSH
- Nyari game yang bagus, tapi spek kurang.
- Ngerjain PR pake laptop
- Maling sinyal Wifi
- Lupa makan
- Di kelas gaada listrik+wifi, kesiksa
- Bawa kabel terminal yang panjang
- Ngayal punya pacar anggota JKT48
- Lagi main, batre habis. Nyari listrik, kaga dapet.
- Punya pacar, ribetnya kaya ngerjain C++
- Otak di overclock, pake heatsink biar dingin
- Presentasi, gurunya gaada. Proyektor dipake nonton Highschool DxD

Sekian dan terimakasih.

Andreas commented on Andrianto Bazzukie's post.
Group: Info Virus Klinik (formely Kocak Gober)
No Application linked* is the screen that is displayed after you unlock* remove/re-insert the battery and type start. I see that everyday. I think it may also be displayed after wiping with JL Commander. Solution: Unplug BB* Open device manager* Open the App Loader. Connect BB without battery* and as soon as you see usb-pin connected click NEXT(must be quick here). You will then be able to select your apps. Just after you hit Finish and the program displays Erasing device* put the battery back in* and all should be good. *copas google -- Salah kamar kaka, ini virus klinik --
